2026-05-04

Scope:
- Restore a stable baseline RAG path as the default.
- Keep finance experimental retrieval available behind an explicit mode switch.
- Do not remove existing safety and infrastructure fixes.

Changed files:
- backend/rag_utils.py
- backend/rag_pipeline.py
- backend/tools.py
- backend/agent.py
- .env.example

Changes:
- Added RAG_RETRIEVAL_MODE with default baseline.
- Baseline mode now uses the stable chunk-level path:
  - global hybrid retrieval
  - rerank
  - auto-merge
  - page_merge context expansion
- Baseline mode does not use query parser filtering, page-level index takeover, or page-level evidence-pack prompt override.
- finance_experimental mode keeps the current page-level/query-parser/evidence-pack path, but it is no longer the default.
- search_knowledge_base now formats baseline results as generic Retrieved Context, while finance_experimental keeps Retrieved Evidence Pack wording.
- Simplified the agent prompt back to general RAG answering behavior so baseline is less over-constrained and less refusal-prone.
- Preserved existing trace and compatibility fields, while exposing retrieval_mode in debug output.
